description:
The PrayerWarriors: All Out For God

Action-Packed FPSC (First Person Spiritual Combat)  3D PC Game. Spiritual Battlefield.

As a prayerwarrior, this action packed game challenges you to go forth into the battlefield of the spiritual realm, find and put on the full Armor of God, and then proceed into dangerous territory on a rescue mission. You will be assisted by E.S.T.H.E.R., a computer that transmits visual data and provides clues that enable the success and the completion of the rescue operation. Choose from various spiritual weapons which you can store in real time as you enter dangerous 3D worlds filled with intelligent enemies. traps, puzzles, and CD Quality interactive stereo settings. Make mission critical decisions, collect scrolls filled with the Word, and pick up objects which randomly generate verses and scriptures. In the final level of the game you will fly Eagle7- a helicopter, find the U.S.S.A.O.F.G. - aircraft carrier, and load up with Truth Rockets. Avoid enemy radar, engage flying enemies, and battle and defeat evil ground forces. In the chopper you can eject at any time and continue the battle on the ground. The game features: Intelligent Enemies, FULL Immersive Virtual Worlds, FLIGHT COMBAT with player eject mode from P.W. helicopter, Awesome 3D Stereo soundtracks, ambient sounds, and Bible Scriptures in all levels which are displayed when the player activates prayer ammo, solves puzzles, and collects scrolls.
